        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/06/2026-06-02-09-33-30-mozilla-central/firefox-153.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:febdd34203b608e9303d4a0c499cb544b1f130960f76d987cef6b6a0a2cbbd487d02adc8243ebdb84b32d24126d2241720e396cad7dc7ed5e64ad3fbefd2e6fa"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/06/2026-06-02-09-33-30-mozilla-central/firefox-153.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
